Class IntentWithResultOnClickListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.tomleese.platinum.callbacks.IntentWithResultOnClickListener

    public class IntentWithResultOnClickListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements android.content.DialogInterface.OnClickListener, android.view.View.OnClickListener
    An OnClickListener that when clicked starts a new intent for a result. Works as both a view listener and a dialog listener.
    Author:
    Tom Leese
